üéØ Interview Quick Revision
Concept	Key Point
JdbcTemplate	Core Spring JDBC class
RowMapper	Maps ResultSet ‚Üí Object
query()	Multiple rows
queryForObject()	Single row
update()	Insert/Update/Delete
@Repository	DAO layer
DataSource	Connection provider